---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Eastcote | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Eastcote. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Eastcote and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:340px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Eastcote</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,54px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Eastcote</h1>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">HA5 · Plastering, skimming &amp; decorating for Eastcote homeowners.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About Eastcote</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Leafy suburban Middlesex — 1930s and 1950s stock with consistent renovation demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Eastcote is sandwiched between Ruislip and Pinner, sharing the same suburban character — largely 1930s semi-detached with some 1950s infill. The housing is well-kept and frequently renovated. Plastering, skimming, and interior decorating during kitchen and bathroom renovations are typical jobs.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Settlement cracking above windows and doors features here as it does across all the London Clay suburbs. Most is cosmetic — treated with a proper plaster repair and skim.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Common problems</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">What goes wrong in Eastcote's housing stock.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Settlement cracks above openings</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Stepped and hairline cracking above windows and doors on the 1930s semis — London Clay movement. Cosmetic in most cases, but it needs a proper repair and skim.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Artex ceilings</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">A lot of the interwar and postwar stock has textured artex ceilings. Overboarding and re-skimming to a flat modern finish is one of our most common Eastcote jobs.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Refit re-skims</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Kitchen and bathroom renovations leave walls patched and uneven. A full re-skim gives a flat, paint-ready surface — the difference between a decent finish and a great one.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Leafy Metro-land around Field End Road.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Eastcote sits between Ruislip and Pinner and shares their character — largely 1930s semi-detached Metro-land with some 1950s infill. The streets around <strong>Field End Road, Eastcote High Road, and Joel Street</strong> are well-kept and frequently renovated, with <strong>Eastcote House Gardens</strong> giving the village a green heart.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">The housing is solid and attractive, and the homeowners tend to be long-term — improving rather than moving. That makes for considered, quality-focused jobs.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Skimming, plastering and decorating.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Eastcote work is renovation-driven: re-skimming after refits, plastering out extensions, treating settlement cracks, overboarding artex, and quality interior painting. Sash and casement repainting comes up on the better-kept houses, and exterior masonry work is scheduled for the warmer, drier months.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Mid-market budgets, high expectations on finish — exactly the kind of work we like to be judged on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Eastcote</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~15 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">A short run from Harefield via Ruislip. A regular local area with no travel premium loaded into the quote.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Easy access</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Wide suburban streets with driveways and on-street parking — straightforward for the van and materials on any job.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Any job size</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">From a single ceiling re-skim to a whole-house renovation. No local job too small.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Dust sheets, protected surfaces, tidy site daily. Fully insured, City &amp; Guilds qualified, no subcontractors.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:0;">
